u_{n}>0
u_{n}\ge u_{n+1},n=1,2,\cdots,\lim_{n\to\infty}u_{n}=0
|\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{n-1}u_{n}-S_{n}|=u_{n+1}-u_{n+2}+\cdots
